        "sender_full_name": "fosco",
        "timestamp": 1620904218
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"282822\">@fosco</span>: I'd take a look at the work of Power and Tanaka on <em>A unified category-theoretic formulation of typed binding signatures</em>. They investigate general notions of substitution monoidal structure that subsumes the operadic versions.</p>",
